Cooperation agreement is signed between ACBA-CREDIT AGRICOLE BANK CJSC and Nature and Biodiversity Conservation Unity (NABU) of Germany, by which it is envisaged to protect the environment with joined forces, and create favourable conditions for the development of ecotourism in the Republic of Armenia.
The following directions of nature conservation projects, activities will be included in the framework of cooperation:
organization and implementation of activities directed to the improvement of ecology studies;
assistance in small and medium enterprises, producing ecoproducts, in the activities on the certification of products;

support to farms and development of ecotourism in Armenia.
